#What is your data science goal.

It is everyone dream that the skill learnt from data science can be used to make discovery from unexplored gathered data, or apply the skill to validate existing discovery.  However like all great tools and skillset, data science can also be used to misrepresent data claims or to paint a different picture as demanded at workplace. Hence data scientists often find themselves balancing their ethical values of showing the honest truth as gleamed from data versus the needs of their employers.
